.Sh NAME
.Nm natacontrol
.Nd NATA device driver control program
.Sh SYNOPSIS
.Nm
.Aq Ar command
.Ar args
.Pp
.Nm
.Ic attach
.Ar channel
.Nm
.Ic detach
